<Layout 
  title="How to Remove Image Background Without Photoshop | Free AI Tool" 
  description="Remove image backgrounds instantly without Photoshop or any software. Our free AI background remover works 100% in your browser — no uploads, no watermarks. Perfect for product photos, portraits, and social media."
  keywords="remove background without photoshop, free background remover, remove image background online, ai background remover free, transparent background without photoshop, remove bg free, product photo background removal, photo cutout tool, remove white background, background eraser online"
>
  <article class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-sm text-accent font-medium mb-4">Design • June 2026 • 4 min read</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white">How to Remove Image Backgrounds Without Photoshop</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8">Photoshop costs $23/month. Canva Pro costs $13/month. But you can <strong>remove image backgrounds</strong> instantly and for free with AI — right inside your browser. No downloads, no signups, no watermarks.</p>

      <div class="border border-border rounded-xl p-6 bg-card/50 mb-8">
