      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Why Remove Backgrounds?</h2>
      <ul class="text-muted-foreground space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>🛍️ <strong>E-commerce product photos</strong> — Amazon, Shopify, and Etsy require clean white backgrounds</li>
        <li>📸 <strong>Profile pictures</strong> — create professional headshots with transparent backgrounds</li>
        <li>🎨 <strong>Design projects</strong> — isolate subjects for collages, thumbnails, and presentations</li>
        <li>📱 <strong>Social media</strong> — create eye-catching posts with custom backgrounds</li>
        <li>📄 <strong>Documents</strong> — clean logo placement and signature extraction</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">How Our AI Background Remover Works</h2>
      <ol class="text-muted-foreground space-y-3 mb-6 list-decimal pl-6">
        <li><strong>Upload your image</strong> — drag and drop or click to browse (PNG, JPG, WebP supported)</li>
        <li><strong>AI processes locally</strong> — a machine learning model runs directly in your browser using WebAssembly</li>
        <li><strong>Download the result</strong> — get a high-resolution PNG with transparent background</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">The entire process takes 2-5 seconds for most images, and <strong>your photo never leaves your device</strong>. This makes it ideal for sensitive images like ID photos, legal documents, or confidential product shots.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">ToolGrid vs. Other Background Removers</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <th class="text-left py-3 font-bold text-white">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 font-bold text-white">ToolGrid</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 font-bold text-white">remove.bg</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 font-bold text-white">Canva</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-border/50"><td class="py-2">Price</td><td class="text-center">Free</td><td class="text-center">$1.99/image</td><td class="text-center">$13/mo</td></tr>
